data.description: You are going to fall in love with this amazing Key West Style custom riverfront pool home with dock and boat lift. Enjoy riverfront living on your huge front porch plus a spacious 2nd floor balcony off the master bedroom. This 2300+ sq ft 3 bedroom 2.5 bath home offers an open floor plan with a spacious living room and dining room with gas fireplace open to the dream kitchen with custom cabinets, stainless steel appliances with oversized range with double oven, a butcher block island plus large breakfast bar. Upstairs you will find the large master bedroom with amazing sunrise views off the balcony. The master bath offers his & her vanities plus make-up area, jacuzzi tub, and walk in shower. All bedrooms offer walk-in closets with great storage. The 2nd & 3rd bedrooms have a jack-n-jill bathroom. The second bedroom offers a murphy bed that is great for guests. Other interior features include fresh paint, plantation shutters throughout, inside laundry and security system. Private screened & heated pool with all brand new salt-water system has a spa and large patio area adjacent for outdoor entertaining. Exterior features include, gated driveway, 2 car garage , covered portico to entryway. Property includes Riparian rights, dock & boathouse for all your water toys! Perfect for jet skis or boat or just fishing off the dock! Great location close to Ormond Mainstreet with restaurants and shopping and a short drive to the beach. Boat launches to the north and south. You will not be disappointed. Rare offering of a newer style property on the river!
